==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[practise]] ([[Commonwealth English]] spelling, used only for the verb)

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-practice.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''practice'''
# [[Repetition]] of an activity to improve [[skill]].  Can be used as noun or verb.
# The ongoing pursuit of a [[craft]] or [[profession]], particularly in the fine arts.
# The observance of [[religious]] duties which a Church requires of its members.

