====Derived terms====
*[[practice makes perfect]]
*[[standard practice]]

===Verb===
# {{US}}: to repeat an activity as a way of improving one's skill.
# To perform or execute a [[craft]] or [[skill]].  
#:''He '''practiced''' law for 19 years.''

